name: {{ .Name }}
version: 0.1.0
categories:
  - Misc
author: Unknown
description: A custom ext_proc extension.
longDescription: |
  A custom ext_proc extension that runs as an out-of-process gRPC server.

  ## Features

  * **Header injection**: Adds a custom response header to every request

  ## Building

  ```bash
  go build -o ext_proc-server .
  ```

  ## Running

  ```bash
  boe run --local .
  ```
type: ext_proc
tags:
  - ext-proc
  - http
  - filter
license: Apache-2.0
extProc:
  grpcPort: 50051
  failureModeAllow: false
  processingMode:
    requestHeaderMode: SKIP
    responseHeaderMode: SEND
    requestBodyMode: NONE
    responseBodyMode: NONE
examples:
  - title: Basic Usage
    description: Run the extension locally
    code: |
      boe run --local .
